{
  "stem": "20088.8",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had really no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whatever food they produced was sent to-- to Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a very cold winter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had no way of heating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they burnt lots of doors, and they burnt furniture, and they eat-- ate even bulbs, tulip bulbs and grass and whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they were not prepared for more mouths to feed and to make it easy now, because they were really organizing themself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was, indeed, it was-- when we got into Amsterdam, there was really nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we didn't realize at first.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But one wonderful thing happened one day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Another transport came from somewhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And on this transport was the daughter of this [INAUDIBLE], who was similar my age.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she had been evacuated or what had gone on those terrible transports from Auschwitz to another camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It might have been even Bergen-Belsen, but I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "No, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Otherwise, she wouldn't have ended up in [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Heuvelland. ?] Anyway, she was liberated somewhere and sent there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she found her mother again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was, of course, you know, wonderful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and we, of course, all hoped that we would-- that Heinz and my father might come as well there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So, you know, every day we waited.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that, I think, that was where we were kind of not so happy there, because we were very anxious.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were very anxious to move on, not to stay there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But, as I say, we couldn't, because there was no way of transport.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And eventually, I think we went on a bus then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Slowly, we made progress up to Amsterdam, first, by bus, and then by train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so we arrived in Amsterdam Central Station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we expected a welcoming committee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
